<emphasis id="F6E0EAECFF816A3EFA5193041906BE4C" bold="true" box="[1453,1798,1373,1406]" pageId="122" pageNumber="880">Status and Conservation.</emphasis>
Classified as Data Deficient on The IUCNRed List. Main threat to the Hairy-tailed Bat is intensive habitat destruction in south-eastern region of 
<collectingRegion id="0650F81CFF816A3EF5D393DC184CBEFF" country="Brazil" name="Sao Paulo" pageId="122" pageNumber="880">Sao Paulo State</collectingRegion>
. Both specimens were collected in protected areas.
</paragraph>
